{"comments":"Polar — 2D polar coordinate system (radius, angle).\n\n## Design Philosophy\n\nPolar coordinates represent 2D points as (radius, angle) pairs:\n- **radius**: distance from origin (non-negative)\n- **angle**: direction from positive X-axis (counter-clockwise)\n\nThis is the natural coordinate system for:\n- Circular UI elements (color wheels, dials, radial menus)\n- Rotational motion and animation\n- Spiral patterns\n\n## Conversion\n\n```purescript\n-- Cartesian (x, y) to Polar (r, θ)\nr = sqrt(x² + y²)\nθ = atan2(y, x)\n\n-- Polar (r, θ) to Cartesian (x, y)\nx = r * cos(θ)\ny = r * sin(θ)\n```\n\n## Dependencies\n\n- Hydrogen.Schema.Geometry.Point (Point2D)\n- Hydrogen.Schema.Geometry.Angle (Degrees, Radians)\n- Data.Number (sqrt, cos, sin, atan2)\n\n## Dependents\n\n- Component.ColorPicker (hue wheel positions)\n- Component.Dial (rotary input)\n- Motion.Spiral (spiral animations)\n","declarations":[{"children":[{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Record"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":["radius",{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Number"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":["angle",{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Geometry","Angle"],"Degrees"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"tag":"REmpty"}],"tag":"RCons"}],"tag":"RCons"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[139,4],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Geometry/Polar.purs","start":[136,20]},"title":"PolarPoint"},{"comments":null,"info":{"declType":"instance","dependencies":[],"type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Data","Eq"],"Eq"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Geometry","Polar"],"PolarPoint"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"sourceSpan":{"end":[141,46],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Geometry/Polar.purs","start":[141,1]},"title"